      "writtenOn": "2020-09-25T20:40:08Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Let\u0027s destruct everything and let the optimizer decide to eliminate the POD ones on our behalf. This also has the advantage of giving us a nice error if we forget to add a kind, rather than accidentally missing a destructor call.\n\n    switch (fKind) {\n        case Kind::kBlock:       reinterpret_cast\u003cBlockData*\u003e(fBytes)-\u003e~BlockData(); break;\n        case Kind::kBoolLiteral: reinterpret_cast\u003cBoolLiteralData*\u003e(fBytes)-\u003e~BoolLiteralData(); break;\n    }",
